# PushomTube 🎬

A beautiful paste-and-click YouTube downloader desktop app.  
Works on **Windows** and **Mac** — no terminal needed.

## Features
- 🎬 Download MP4, WebM, MP3, WAV
- 📺 Quality up to 4K
- 📁 Choose your save folder
- 📋 One-click paste from clipboard
- 📊 Real-time progress bar
- 🗂 Auto-opens folder when done

## Download the App
Go to the **Actions** tab → click the latest build → scroll down to **Artifacts** → download for your platform:
- **PushomTube-Mac.zip** → for Mac users
- **PushomTube-Windows.zip** → for Windows users

